
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Requirement Analysis - Solution Requirements</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Requirement Analysis - Solution Requirements</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>Functional Requirements (FR)</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>FR ID</th><th>Epic / Module</th><th>Sub-Requirement / Functional Rule</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>FR-1</b></td>
            <td>Catalog & Filtering</td>
            <td>
                - Display vintage items with discount badges and stock indicators.<br>
                - Filter items by category, price ranges, and sorting (ratings, prices).
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>FR-2</b></td>
            <td>Flipping Payment Gateway</td>
            <td>
                - Input card details showing a live-updating credit card card layout.<br>
                - Flip card on CVV focus. Simulate secure authorization loop logs.
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>FR-3</b></td>
            <td>Seller Dashboard Metrics</td>
            <td>
                - Display sales totals in Rupees (₹), total orders, and unit tracking.<br>
                - Trigger inventory low-stock alerts and manage catalog items (CRUD).
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>FR-4</b></td>
            <td>Interactive Profile Manager</td>
            <td>
                - Allow accounts to update full names, emails, and passwords safely.
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>Non-Functional Requirements (NFR)</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>NFR ID</th><th>Requirement</th><th>Description & Implementation</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>NFR-1</b></td>
            <td>Usability</td>
            <td>Cozy visual layout with clear tactile feedbacks and responsive viewports.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>NFR-2</b></td>
            <td>Security</td>
            <td>Bcrypt hashing of user passwords; JWT security tokens inside request headers.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>NFR-3</b></td>
            <td>Reliability</td>
            <td>Global error catches and async handlers to prevent app crashes.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>NFR-4</b></td>
            <td>Scalability</td>
            <td>Three-tier architecture separating endpoints, validations, and databases.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    </body>
    </html>
    